lead_paragraph: England captain Alastair Cook won the toss and unsurprisingly decided to bat against India in the third match of the five-test series at the Punjab Cricket Association (PCA) Stadium in Mohali on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: England Bat in Mohali, Nair Makes India Debut
